eventsAnnotated.name: 2013 Bohol Earthquake (646)
eventsAnnotated.description: The 2013 Bohol earthquake occurred on October 15 at 8:12:31 PST in Bohol, an island province located in Central Visayas, Philippines. The magnitude of the earthquake was recorded at Mw 7.2, with epicenter 6 kilometres (3.7 mi) S 24° W of Sagbayan. <a href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2013_Bohol_earthquake' target='_blank'>Wikipedia Page<a>

eventsAnnotated.name: 2016 Fort McMurray Wildfire E(500)
eventsAnnotated.description: On May 1, 2016, a wildfire began southwest of Fort McMurray, Alberta, Canada. On May 3, it swept through the community, forcing the largest wildfire evacuation in Alberta's history, with upwards of 88,000 people forced from their homes. <a href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2016_Fort_McMurray_wildfire' target='_blank'>Wikipedia Page<a>
